  (text "HiveSync Entrance Monitor Schematic\nESP32-S3 + OV5640 + IR LEDs + CC1101 + ICS-43434 + SHT40\n\nCamera on DVP interface (8-bit parallel)\nIR LEDs on GPIO (NPN driver)\nCC1101 on SPI\nICS-43434 on I2S\nSHT40 on I2C\nSD card on SPI2\nPower: 18650 + 2W solar" (at 200 200) (uuid text1))
